metadata.name: Escape #1/7
metadata.description: Surrounded by huge concrete walls, we are looking for escape, a dream of true freedom, to fly towards the light freed from all constraint. This cooling tower is one of the largest we have been able to explore to date, the impression of being so tiny, staring at this circle of light coming from the top, a silence broken by an incredible echo at the slightest sound. An incredible exploration.
